'''毛律山'''（{{lang-ms|Gunung Murud}}; {{lang-en|Mount Murud}}）是坐落于[[婆罗洲|婆罗洲]][[马来西亚|马来西亚]]境内的[[砂岩|砂岩质]]山脉，其高度海拔2423米，是[[东马|东马]][[砂拉越州|砂拉越州]]的最高峰。<ref>Beaman, J. H., and C. Anderson. 1997. The summit flora of Mt. Murud, Sarawak, Malaysia. ''Contributions from the University of Michigan Herbarium'' 21: 85-141.</ref><ref>Beaman, J.H. 1999. {{PDFlink|[http://www.arbec.com.my/pdf/art3mayjun99.pdf Preliminary Enumeration Of The Summit Flora, Mount Murud, Kelabit Highlands, Sarawak.]|99.4 [[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 101826 bytes -->}} ''ASEAN Review of Biodiversity and Environmental Conservation'': 1–23.</ref>

毛律山山顶地区特有的热带[[食虫植物|食虫植物]]——[[毛律山猪笼草|毛律山猪笼草]]（''Nepenthes murudensis''）就是以毛律山的名字命名的。<ref name=J&C>Jebb, M.H.P. & M.R. Cheek 1997. [[猪笼草属（猪笼草科）的框架性修订|A skeletal revision of ''Nepenthes'' (Nepenthaceae)]]. ''Blumea'' '''42'''(1): 1–106.</ref><ref>De Witte, J. 1996. {{PDFlink|[http://carnivorousplants.org/cpn/articles/CPNv25n2p41_45.pdf ''Nepenthes'' of Gunung Murud.]|567 [[Kibibyte|KiB]]<!-- application/pdf, 581107 bytes -->}} ''[[食虫植物通讯|Carnivorous Plant Newsletter]]'' '''25'''(2): 41–45.</ref>

